body:
✨Lemons and midnight conversations✨

Part 3 - “3 for 2”

(Cyrus’s pov)

It started to get really dark now but the streetlights lid up the street. We were walking in the middle of the street because there weren’t any cars around. It was really quite. The only thing you could hear was our footsteps and some teens laughing in the distance. And if I listened closely could I hear TJ’s breath. He was breathing pretty heavy because it was a little colder outside than it usually is.

“So I have my horror movies, what is your thing Kippen?”

“Well basketball obviously. But I guess I like to draw too”

“Oh wow, really? I did not expect TJ Kippen to be an artsy boy” I gave him a friendly punch on the arm to tease him.

“Hey! I like to draw a little does that automatically mean I’m an ‘artsy’ tumblr boy?”

“Not really, but I will from now on call you 'artsy tumblr boy”

“Oh my god” TJ tried to sound annoyed but I could see that he laughed.

“Or wait even better” TJ almost looked terrified

“I shall call you Scary artsy basketball tumblr guy” Said I with a over dramatic voice and my arms in the air.

“That’s not even a real sentence”

“I like it”

We kept walking to the store while talking about everything from tumblr to whales (don’t ask)

“We’re finally here!” I started running towards the supermarket when I saw it. “I’m coming chocolate chocolate chip muffin!”

I could almost feel TJ laughing embarrassed behind me.

(No ones pov)

TJ and Cyrus came in to the store. It wasn’t a lot of people there, only an old lady and a dad with his two daughters.

“So what do you want Underdog?”

“Well about 50 chocolate chocolate chip muffins-” Said Cyrus sarcastic even tho he actually wasn’t really joking.

“No but I need my daily dose of chocolate so that is a must. What do you want?”

“Blueberry macadamia”

“Huh?” Cyrus looked pretty confused.

TJ just laughed it of and started walking further in to the store.

“Cheese puffs?” TJ was pointing at a pack of cheese puffs.

“Sure”

They kept walking, it was a pretty big store and the chocolate chocolate chip muffins was in the back so they had to walk for a while.

“So you haven’t told anyone about what you feel…for him?” TJ hesitated a little he didn’t want to make Cyrus uncomfortable.

“No” Cyrus was looking down at his feets

“No one knows besides you and my diary”

“I’m honored to be the first person you told”

“Well technically you’re the second person I told because I told my diary first”

TJ gave Cyrus a light push on his back to tease him. They both laughed for like the 500th time just this night.

“Well here’s your beloved chocolate chocolate chip muffin” They had reached the back of the store where all the muffins were. Cyrus looked at the chocolate chocolate chip muffin like it was a newborn puppy.

“Oh boy that’s gonna taste GOOD”

Cyrus took two muffins and put them in a bag.

As they walked towards the exits, TJ stopped because he saw something. He did some kind of weird walk-run thing towards the thing that catch his eyes. Cyrus looked pretty confused when TJ just went to the right without saying anything.

“Lemons!” TJ was holding up one lemon in each hand. Cyrus had followed him.

“Really, lemons?” Cyrus sounded pretty sceptical.

“It’s 3 for 2!” TJ was right, there was a sign that said 'lemons 3 for 2’

“But lemons?”

“Why not?”

Cyrus thought for a second.

“Sure” TJ got a smile on his face that looked like a kid on Christmas.

“Go for it!” Cyrus made thums up.

“Yes!!!!!”

They paid and exited the store.

“Where should we go now?” TJ asked.

“The park again?”

“Sure”

summary: Our Gay soft sporty boi? (aka tj)
question: Our Gay soft sporty boi? (aka tj)
answer:
Actually, I’ve done our beloved gay soft sporty boy right over here, but yknow let’s do five more good qualities and three more bad qualities just because why not~ And another headcanon bc why not :P

The rest I don’t think I can reanswer though oops

  • 5 good qualities: he is amazing dyscalculic representation, he‘s able to recognize and admit when he’s done wrong, he has like the second best redemption arc I’ve ever seen, he’s pretty creative (rapped for Buffy, somersault costume idea), he SOFT
  • 3 bad qualities: he’s had the same hairstyle since he was like 6, he hasn’t reconciled with Marty (and idk if he has time to anymore episode wise), he’s not in enough episodes
  • head canon: he knows all the Hamilton songs and can flawlessly spit all the lyrics to “My Shot” (because I like to headcanon he likes history too, so history + rapping? totally hamilton geek)

Send me a character ask!

  • 3 bad qualities: he’s had the same hairstyle since he was like 6, he hasn’t reconciled with Marty (and idk if he has time to anymore episode wise), he’s not in enough episodes
  • head canon: he knows all the Hamilton songs and can flawlessly spit all the lyrics to “My Shot” (because I like to headcanon he likes history too, so history + rapping? totally hamilton geek)
